      <title>智方桌宠开发手记（一）——电脑状态上传至MQTT服务器</title>
      <link href="/2023/06/01/%E6%99%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%8C%E5%AE%A0%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%89%8B%E8%AE%B0%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E8%87%B3MQTT%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/"/>
      <url>/2023/06/01/%E6%99%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%8C%E5%AE%A0%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%89%8B%E8%AE%B0%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E8%87%B3MQTT%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="智方桌宠开发手记（一）——电脑状态上传至MQTT服务器"><a href="#智方桌宠开发手记（一）——电脑状态上传至MQTT服务器" class="headerlink" title="智方桌宠开发手记（一）——电脑状态上传至MQTT服务器"></a>智方桌宠开发手记（一）——电脑状态上传至MQTT服务器</h1><p><a href="https://reaperwlllll.github.io/2023/06/01/%E6%99%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%8C%E5%AE%A0%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%89%8B%E8%AE%B0%EF%BC%88%E3%80%87%EF%BC%89%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E7%BC%98%E8%B5%B7%E4%B8%8E%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B/">智方桌宠开发手记（〇）——缘起与简介</a></p><hr><p>主要参考资料：<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/tardis/zm/art/469956102?source_id=1005">基于Arduino打造DIY极客电脑性能监控系统</a>，<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42487906/article/details/119990801">基于AIDA64的电脑性能监控</a></p><hr><p>如何在电脑运行的时候不用打开任务管理器就能获取电脑状态呢，如何让平平无奇的一个小方块看上去b格很高呢？远程状态监视站是个一石二鸟的好东西！</p><p>这并不是一件难以实现的事情，经过在简中互联网的一番*里淘金，大致确定了以下实现步骤。</p><ol><li>获取电脑状态</li><li>将电脑状态上传至本地端口或上传至mqtt服务器</li><li>esp32获取并解析状态数据，显示到屏幕上</li></ol><p>理论成立，开始实践。首先使用开源软件<a href="https://openhardwaremonitor.org/">Open Hardware Monitor</a>获取电脑状态信息。虽然理论上AIDA64更高级功能也更多一些，但是貌似AIDA64对AMD的支持并不是十分之好，一直获取不到CPU的占用率，遂换用OHM。</p><p><img src="/.%5Cimage%5Cmonitor.png" alt="OHM"></p><p>在第一篇参考资料中，作者是使用python脚本直接从OPM中获取信息，这部分属于我的知识盲区，未敢复现。遂另辟蹊径，在OPM中有一个功能：Remote Web Server。使能这个选项后即可在本地端口上通过web界面查看各状态。</p><p><img src="G:\blog\source_posts\image\remote.png" alt="Remote Web Server"></p><p><img src="G:\blog\source_posts\image\web_UI.png" alt="web界面"></p><p>理论上此时通过端口映射就可以实现远程的状态监控，然而这并不是本项目需要完成的内容。倘若只需实现局域网内的状态监视的话，到这一步就足够了。esp32可以访问这个端口并解析数据。但只局限于局域网的状态传输显然不够优雅，且OPM貌似不支持选择性输出数据（AIDA64可以），因此esp32获取并解析这些数据可能会浪费部分的资源，并丢失一定的实时性。因此需要在电脑端就筛选出需要的数据，并打包上传至MQTT服务器，这样esp32只需要订阅一个topic就可以获取电脑的状态。</p><p>数据处理那还是python给力，遂决定编写一个脚本来完成数据的获取、处理、和发送。查看浏览器后台发现web每次刷新时都会请求一次data.json</p><p><img src="G:\blog\source_posts\image\dataJson.png" alt="dataJson"></p><p>查看data.json发现里面确实包含了所有需要的数据。</p><p><img src="G:\blog\source_posts\image\data.png" alt="dataTxt"></p><p>python可以通过jsonpath很方便快捷的筛选出想要的数据，因此定义函数。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">getData</span>(<span class="params">dictionary,<span class="built_in">id</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#通过id获取想要数据的父级</span></span><br><span class="line">    temp = jsonpath.jsonpath(dictionary, <span class="string">&#x27;$..[?(@.id==%d)]&#x27;</span> % <span class="built_in">id</span>) </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#获取所需数据</span></span><br><span class="line">    Value = jsonpath.jsonpath(temp,<span class="string">&#x27;$..Value&#x27;</span>)[<span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> Value</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>通过此函数筛选出我想要的数据</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#新建一个json包含五个数据</span></span><br><span class="line">labtop = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;cpuTemp&quot;</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;cpuUsed&quot;</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;memoryUsed&quot;</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;memoryUsedData&quot;</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;gpuUsed&quot;</span>: <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#数据发送</span></span><br><span class="line">timeNow=time.time()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> timeNow-lastUpdateTime&gt;<span class="number">3</span>:<span class="comment">#3s发送一次</span></span><br><span class="line">    lastUpdateTime=timeNow</span><br><span class="line">    f = req.urlopen(<span class="string">&#x27;http://192.168.137.1:8085/data.json&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    data = json.loads(f.read().decode(<span class="string">&#x27;utf-8&#x27;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">    cpuTemp = getData(data,<span class="number">15</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    cpuUsed = getData(data,<span class="number">17</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    memoryUsed = getData(data,<span class="number">39</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    memoryUsedData = getData(data,<span class="number">41</span>) </span><br><span class="line">    gpuUsed = getData(data,<span class="number">72</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">##将上述五个数据打包成json格式发送</span></span><br><span class="line">    labtop[<span class="string">&quot;cpuTemp&quot;</span>] = cpuTemp</span><br><span class="line">    labtop[<span class="string">&quot;cpuUsed&quot;</span>] = cpuUsed</span><br><span class="line">    labtop[<span class="string">&quot;memoryUsed&quot;</span>] = memoryUsed</span><br><span class="line">    labtop[<span class="string">&quot;memoryUsedData&quot;</span>] = memoryUsedData</span><br><span class="line">    labtop[<span class="string">&quot;gpuUsed&quot;</span>] = gpuUsed</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#publish json包，此处+/set向除本机外所有设备推送数据</span></span><br><span class="line">    client.publish(bemfaTopic+<span class="string">&quot;/set&quot;</span>, json.dumps(labtop))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>自此电脑的性能数据已经上传至mqtt服务器，esp32只需要解析json包就可以直接获取。</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">bemfa_callback</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">char</span> *topic, byte *payload, <span class="type">unsigned</span> <span class="type">int</span> length)</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  dataFlag = <span class="literal">false</span>;<span class="comment">//接收到数据后，将数据接收标志位置为false</span></span><br><span class="line">  Serial.print(<span class="string">&quot;Topic:&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  Serial.println(topic);</span><br><span class="line">  String msg = <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; length; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    msg += (<span class="type">char</span>)payload[i];</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  DynamicJsonDocument <span class="title function_">doc</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">1024</span>)</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  deserializeJson(doc, msg);</span><br><span class="line">  cpuTemp = doc[<span class="string">&quot;cpuTemp&quot;</span>].as&lt;String&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">  cpuLoad = doc[<span class="string">&quot;cpuUsed&quot;</span>].as&lt;String&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">  gpuLoad = doc[<span class="string">&quot;gpuUsed&quot;</span>].as&lt;String&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">  memoryLoad = doc[<span class="string">&quot;memoryUsed&quot;</span>].as&lt;String&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">  memoryUsed = doc[<span class="string">&quot;memoryUsedData&quot;</span>].as&lt;String&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">  dataFlag = <span class="literal">true</span>;<span class="comment">//数据接收完成，将数据接收标志位置为true,防止lvgl和mqtt同时操作数据</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>现在只要电脑上OPM和脚本都在运行，esp32还有网的话，在哪都能看到电脑状态啦！理论上只需要给脚本加上开机自启和自动打开OPM，就可以监测有没有好室友偷玩你的电脑，嘻嘻。</p><p>目前实现效果如图：(tft屏幕目测和拍出来差别还是挺大的)</p><p><img src="/.%5Cimage%5ClabtopData.jpg" alt="远程状态监视"></p><p>mqtt服务器可以自己架设，也可以使用巴法云、阿里云等云端mqtt，目前我使用的是巴法云，毕竟没什么设备需要管理，巴法云足够了。</p><p>脚本代码完整代码在此，mqtt的部分可以参考巴法云官方例程<a href="https://bbs.bemfa.com/81">python 接入，mqtt和tcp - 巴法开放论坛 (bemfa.com)</a>。还有很多可以完善的地方，欢迎大佬教我更为优雅的实现方式~</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># %%</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># coding=utf-8</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> urllib.request <span class="keyword">as</span> req</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> json</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> jsonpath</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> paho.mqtt.client <span class="keyword">as</span> mqtt</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> time</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">HOST = <span class="string">&quot;bemfa.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">PORT = <span class="number">9501</span></span><br><span class="line">client_id = <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="comment">#自己的巴法云私钥</span></span><br><span class="line">bemfaTopic = <span class="string">&quot;labtopData&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">lastUpdateTime = time.time()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#新建一个json包含五个数据</span></span><br><span class="line">labtop = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;cpuTemp&quot;</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;cpuUsed&quot;</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;memoryUsed&quot;</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;memoryUsedData&quot;</span>: <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;gpuUsed&quot;</span>: <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">on_connect</span>(<span class="params">client, userdata, flags, rc</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Connected with result code &quot;</span>+<span class="built_in">str</span>(rc))</span><br><span class="line">    client.subscribe(bemfaTopic)         <span class="comment"># 订阅消息</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#消息接收</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">on_message</span>(<span class="params">client, userdata, msg</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;主题:&quot;</span>+msg.topic+<span class="string">&quot; 消息:&quot;</span>+<span class="built_in">str</span>(msg.payload.decode(<span class="string">&#x27;utf-8&#x27;</span>)))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#订阅成功</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">on_subscribe</span>(<span class="params">client, userdata, mid, granted_qos</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;On Subscribed: qos = %d&quot;</span> % granted_qos)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 失去连接</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">on_disconnect</span>(<span class="params">client, userdata, rc</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> rc != <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Unexpected disconnection %s&quot;</span> % rc)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">f = req.urlopen(<span class="string">&#x27;本地端口/data.json&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">data = json.loads(f.read().decode(<span class="string">&#x27;utf-8&#x27;</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># print(data)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># print(type(data))</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">getData</span>(<span class="params">dictionary,<span class="built_in">id</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">    temp = jsonpath.jsonpath(dictionary, <span class="string">&#x27;$..[?(@.id==%d)]&#x27;</span> % <span class="built_in">id</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    Value = jsonpath.jsonpath(temp,<span class="string">&#x27;$..Value&#x27;</span>)[<span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> Value</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># %%</span></span><br><span class="line">client = mqtt.Client(client_id)</span><br><span class="line">client.username_pw_set(<span class="string">&quot;userName&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;passwd&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">client.on_connect = on_connect</span><br><span class="line">client.on_message = on_message</span><br><span class="line">client.on_subscribe = on_subscribe</span><br><span class="line">client.on_disconnect = on_disconnect</span><br><span class="line">client.connect(HOST, PORT, <span class="number">60</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> <span class="literal">True</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    client.loop_start()</span><br><span class="line">    timeNow=time.time()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> timeNow-lastUpdateTime&gt;<span class="number">3</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        lastUpdateTime=timeNow</span><br><span class="line">        f = req.urlopen(<span class="string">&#x27;本地端口/data.json&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        data = json.loads(f.read().decode(<span class="string">&#x27;utf-8&#x27;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        cpuTemp = getData(data,<span class="number">15</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        cpuUsed = getData(data,<span class="number">17</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        memoryUsed = getData(data,<span class="number">39</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        memoryUsedData = getData(data,<span class="number">41</span>) </span><br><span class="line">        gpuUsed = getData(data,<span class="number">72</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">##将上述五个数据打包成json格式发送</span></span><br><span class="line">        labtop[<span class="string">&quot;cpuTemp&quot;</span>] = cpuTemp</span><br><span class="line">        labtop[<span class="string">&quot;cpuUsed&quot;</span>] = cpuUsed</span><br><span class="line">        labtop[<span class="string">&quot;memoryUsed&quot;</span>] = memoryUsed</span><br><span class="line">        labtop[<span class="string">&quot;memoryUsedData&quot;</span>] = memoryUsedData</span><br><span class="line">        labtop[<span class="string">&quot;gpuUsed&quot;</span>] = gpuUsed</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">#publish json包</span></span><br><span class="line">        client.publish(bemfaTopic+<span class="string">&quot;/set&quot;</span>, json.dumps(labtop))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    client.loop_stop()</span><br><span class="line">    time.sleep(<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
